Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(181,32)\fad(500,500)\3cD99437\blur4\b1}#16「我最喜欢巨型机器人」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「造出属于我们自己的机器人」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们已经制造出了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基于这个理念  并汇聚了大家的想法的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常感谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说…锵锵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是Gunvarrel制造计划试制2号机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简称Gun制造2号机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20\fad(200,0)}宇宙糖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头上贴的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我小小的抵抗的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器人不需要脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸才是机器人的命根子好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个问题不是已经讨论过并得出结论了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说你能拿出让我信服的反驳意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能的话  我倒是可以听一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  小亚希…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始启动测试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  天王寺小姐还没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监督者不在的时候是不能动机器人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是说明一下的话是没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机师  八汐学长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副机师  大德学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱动系统负责人  古郡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…拒…拒绝！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是如此  请继续
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试制2号机的最大特征就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用了磁单极子驱动器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此运动性能完全凌驾于1号机之上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操作方式为通过Killballad系统进行遥控
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是磁单极子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到在那之后  每天早上都会掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还有一个1号机所没有的装置需要操作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…  激光供电装置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大…大炮？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说把电能转化成激光来进行供电吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也是由海和淳负责
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要注意的是不能对着人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便问一下  要是照射到了人身上会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇哇  这…这种事情  我做不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说这也实在是有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:05:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧  有安全装置的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有瞄准在抛物面天线上的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会进行照射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海很擅长这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我擅长的是格斗游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射击游戏的话…类型有点微妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  绹小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  会议延长到了现在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会议？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期天还要开会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  开始启动测试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight  哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像…像这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  发射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电  电池  充填  完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴  把它放下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否进行启动测试的最终判断
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绹小姐  交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  启动测试  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电源启动  起重机关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空空荡荡四处漏风Gunvarrel  顺利启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OS  运转正常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激光扫描仪  展开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松开吊索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  海  迈出值得纪念的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那我先试试前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gunvarrel  出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害  真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全无法想象出这是高中生制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然没有看错你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  绹小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:09:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不得不请各位在下周离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说之前开了个会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是相隔五年后种子岛又决定要发射火箭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以出于安保方面的考虑  不能再把这里借给各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本公司所制造的动力服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs16\fad(0,500)}「动力服失控事故」本月28日开始审判
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs16\fad(500,0)}艾克索斯克尔顿公司  太阳风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吸取了15年崩坏的教训
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用于抵抗太阳风暴带来的电磁脉冲的防护措施可谓万无一失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请问去年夏天发生的失控事故究竟是什么原因导致的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法庭正在针对这个问题进行审理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时我真的弄不明白部长究竟是厉害还是不厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是她向世博委员会提交的资料视频
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是中央种子岛高中机器人研究部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长  濑乃宫亚希穗  18岁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨型机器人是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨型机器人是大家的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨型机器人是孩子们的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨型机器人是正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢巨型机器人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明自从国会议事堂恐怖袭击事件之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gunvarrel的形象变得很差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们对机器人的看法也更加严苛了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希只是不会动摇而已
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GEZI姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  八汐先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我今天的候补搜索地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  君岛报告书No.7
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的候补搜索地如下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝满神社  熊野海岸  门仓岬…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭又要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go  Hot Dog Go
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海  你如果也是个男孩子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(371,325)\fs16}Right Stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去成为拥有独有的正确资质的男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一堆废铜烂铁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了君岛晃的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最近几个月种子岛上的微博历史记录
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很快就被删除了  但确实有一条记录提到了君岛晃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发言者是大德淳和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指示其删除的人是八汐海翔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该有吩咐过让你去调查他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你想说自己看漏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他似乎不仅是你的学弟  还是你妹妹的好友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是说我在包庇他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有必要的话  我可以去把他「做掉」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长深田老师可真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…  好想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八汐同学呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去接他的时候他已经不在家了  究竟上哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神  神代同学  你走光啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴  你可不准偷看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我才不会看喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是荒谬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an7\pos(270,59)\fs14\frz-13.5\bord1.5}标题  告知亚希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an7\pos(265,77)\fs14\frz-13.5\bord1.5}发件人  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an7\pos(120,85)\fs16\frz-16\1c707070\bord0}小充打电话跟我说他会晚点到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是让它走两步而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为距离下一阶段的审核已经没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太奇怪了  刚才明明没有的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:13:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GEZI姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是君岛报告书No.7没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要下载吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到这一步了  只能上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GEZI姐  下载…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞榎小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小充好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊  大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日高同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大德学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  机器人在行走的时候有点不协调
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不协调？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在抬脚的时候感觉有一瞬间会变得很僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是驱动的齿轮有缺口了吗  你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长  拜托你操作一下激光枪座
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞榎小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说过让你不要多管闲事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就此收手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…  你是在说君岛报告书的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别废话  老老实实按我说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说…  君岛晃的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞榎小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,125)\fs18\frz-15\bord0\shad2}未知号码
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(260,160)\fs10\frz-15\bord0\shad2}来电中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是有些僵硬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是供电有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系统一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呜哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  神代同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笼中鸟…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪  瑞榎小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞榎小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话还没说完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海  不好意思  能帮我一把吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这玩意好像出了点故障
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停不下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停不下来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞榎小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(425,170)\fs14\bord1.5}禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请问去年夏天发生的失控事故究竟是什么原因导致的呢
